# from lcapy import Circuit
import ngspyce as ng

def print_op(show_ib=True, show_ie=False):
  op = ng.operating_point()
  for k in sorted(op.keys()):
    if '[i' in k or '#branch' in k:
        if '[is]' in k:
            continue
        if '[ie]' in k and not show_ie:
            continue
        if '[ib]' in k and not show_ib:
            continue
        current = op[k][0]
        k = k.replace('q.x.', '')
        k = k.replace('r.x.', '')
        if abs(current) > 1e-6:
            print('%10s = %8.3f uA' % (k, 1e6*current))
        else:
            print('%10s = %8.3f nanoA' % (k, 1e9*current))
    elif '[g' in k:
        gm = op[k][0]
        if gm > 10e-3:
            print('%10s = %8.3f mS' % (k, 1e3 * gm))
        else:
            print('%10s = %8.3f uS' % (k, 1e6 * gm))
    else:  # Voltage
        voltage = op[k][0]
        k = k.replace('x.', '')
        if abs(voltage) > 10e-3:
            print('%10s = %8.4f V' % (k, voltage))
        else:
            print('%10s = %8.1f uV' % (k, 1e6*voltage))


def diff_op(lhs, rhs, show_ie=False):
  for k in sorted(lhs.keys()):
    old = lhs[k][0]
    new = rhs[k][0]
    if k[0] == '@' or '#branch' in k:
        delta = new - old
        if np.abs(delta) < 1e-9:
            continue
        if '[ie]' in k and not show_ie:
            continue
        k = k.replace('q.x.', '')
        k = k.replace('r.x.', '')
        if delta < 1e-6:
            print('%15s %10.3f uA, %10.3f uA, delta %10.3f nanoA' %
              (k, old * 1e6, new * 1e6, (new - old) * 1e9))
        else:
            print('%15s %10.3f uA, %10.3f uA, delta %10.3f uA' %
              (k, old * 1e6, new * 1e6, (new - old) * 1e6))
    else:
        delta = new - old
        k = k.replace('x.', '')
        if delta < 1e-3:
            print('%15s %10.3f mV, %10.3f mV, delta %10.3f uV' %
              (k, old * 1e3, new * 1e3, (new - old)* 1e6))
        else:
            print('%15s %10.3f mV, %10.3f mV, delta %10.3f milliV' %
              (k, old * 1e3, new * 1e3, (new - old)* 1e3))


def para(r1, r2):
  return (r1*r2) / (r1 + r2)

基本参数 $\newcommand{\li}[1]{{i_\mathrm{#1}}}$ $\newcommand{\ui}[1]{{I_\mathrm{#1}}}$ $\newcommand{\lv}[1]{{v_\mathrm{#1}}}$ $\newcommand{\uv}[1]{{V_\mathrm{#1}}}$ $\newcommand{\sm}[2]{{{#1}_\mathrm{#2}}}$

跨导 $g_\mathrm{m}=\dfrac{I_\mathrm{C}}{V_\mathrm{T}}$

输入动态电阻 $r_\pi = \dfrac{\beta_0}{g_\mathrm{m}}$

输出动态电阻 $r_o=\dfrac{1}{\ui{C}}(\uv{A}+\uv{CE})\approx\dfrac{V_A}{I_C}$

Current source¶

$\sm{g}{m} = \dfrac{1\mathrm{mA}}{26\mathrm{mV}} = \dfrac{1}{26\Omega}$

$r_o\approx\dfrac{V_A}{I_C} = \dfrac{150\mathrm{V}}{1\mathrm{mA}}=$150kΩ

Emitter degenaration¶

$\sm{R}{out}=\sm{r}{o}+(\sm{g}{m}\sm{r}{o}+1)(\sm{R}{E}/\!/r_\pi)$

跨导 $g_\mathrm{m}=\dfrac{I_\mathrm{C}}{V_\mathrm{T}}$

输入动态电阻 $r_\pi = \dfrac{\beta_0}{g_\mathrm{m}}$

输出动态电阻 $r_o=\dfrac{1}{\ui{C}}(\uv{A}+\uv{CE})\approx\dfrac{V_A}{I_C}$

本征增益 $\sm{g}{m}\sm{r}{o} = \dfrac{\uv{A}}{\uv{T}}\gg 1$

$\sm{R}{out}\approx\sm{r}{o}+\sm{g}{m}\sm{r}{o}(\sm{R}{E}/\!/r_\pi)$

$\sm{R}{out}\approx\sm{r}{o}(1+ \sm{g}{m}(\sm{R}{E}/\!/r_\pi))$

Emitter degeneration¶

$A =\dfrac{\sm{R}{C}}{1/\sm{g}{m}+\sm{R}{E}} \approx \dfrac{R_\mathrm{C}}{R_\mathrm{E}}$

Copied! 
%%tikz -ct
